{"tid":271290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"色慾校服情侶　平台公然互摷","createTime":"2017-06-05T03:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T12:07:21.000Z","uid":28366,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69869e11ff24383e3df622041b1f6c0e333b8e23","tid":271290,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20070131/large/31ls1p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070131%2Flarge%2F31ls1p6.jpg&h=db43f50e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">一對穿校服小情侶在屋苑的平台上纏綿。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n少男少女情竇初開，拍拖之際情到濃時，或許不能自我控制，出現激情行為。近日就有網民直擊身穿校服的學生情侶公然在公園纏綿，雙方手口並用，行為大膽開放令人側目，不少網民看過照片後嘩然，批評學生德育水平每下愈況。 <br />\n<br />\n「個男仔係咁搞，個女仔係度扮到欲拒還迎，點知最後個女仔主動番，好彩係佢除衫之前有保安員行過，唔係真係無眼睇！」 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">少男將手伸入裙內</span></span><br />\n<br />\n網民 atvreality在香港討論區發放多幅相片和短片，內容都是一對校服情侶的纏綿情況，男生穿藍色冷衫、灰色長褲，女學生則是一條藍色連身校裙，繫上紅色領帶。<br />\n<br />\n由照片可見，該對學生情侶纏綿時非常肉緊，女方躺在男方大腿上，男方一度將手伸入女方裙內。「佢不顧樓上或附近大廈有住戶，公然於屋苑平台互相挑逗。」網友 atvreality形容兩人敗壞道德風氣。<br />\n<br />\n這幾張激情照片激發網民議論，批評兩人不知廉恥，「好激呀！家情侶真係開放。」網民 happy1202則說：「點解家後生仔女會搞成咁，我真係要好好睇實我個女先得呀！」<br />\n<br />\n育評議會副主席何漢權認為近年中學生行為問題越來越嚴重，這對小情侶行為越軌，師長應輔導他們建立健康價值觀，如有需要應報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20070131/6768807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20070131%2F6768807&d=Ld41p4dMG8YQK9vUD09cBC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ee6e0bec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20070131%2F6768807&h=8b11cd2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20070131/6768807</a>"},{"pid":"2cdc56cb6d7db0f0072c023404aec579a1764cd6","tid":271290,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"樓主你好撚悶咩？"},{"pid":"52813cf56789e6c3d333f7cec0f9596d42c1f840","tid":271290,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:23:53.000Z","msg":"咁就十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41f16e1d7d3792c5fcfba5f2d2dc73061efcbe3","tid":271290,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁就十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e297858d48d526e1e3bf31cc322991fb161feff","tid":271290,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:25:15.000Z","msg":"好福氣做人老母 過多十年可能孫都有件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b24477b8b133a2da51357ed8ac44a15c5422282","tid":271290,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"樓主悶成到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150ceba03655ab24ee32b56ef4f55e8a588d5228","tid":271290,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:29:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主悶成到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91b1b4f245f5c4bf482ed17f05e30d3d626f53f","tid":271290,"uid":70227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:29:41.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪啱啱出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d4ffca24931d4a6b4185045f8bab25eed0b924","tid":271290,"uid":36291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:34:57.000Z","msg":"主修考古?"},{"pid":"9908db43d2c4e219f50615e5b9b81e9d0